General.Name: Rhom Bho Property Public Company Limited
General.Description: Rhom Bho Property Public Company Limited operates as a property development company in Thailand. It engages in the development and sale of residential condominiums. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand. Rhom Bho Property Public Company Limited operates as a subsidiary of Hutajuta group.
